<span id="freeTextContainer6301087549622641343">I read this almost 35 years ago, as a preteen, and I believe it was about 15 or so years after it was published in the 70s. Pre-Internet, it was helpf</span>
  <span id="freeText6301087549622641343" style="display:none">I read this almost 35 years ago, as a preteen, and I believe it was about 15 or so years after it was published in the 70s. Pre-Internet, it was helpful to read a book that discussed real issues. That said, from what I remember, I don't think this book has aged well and most young girls today would find it to be practically archaic.</span>
